*   ## **_Lashley def. Toa Liona_**
    

The match that saw Bobby Lashley give Toa a LOT of offense

Post match, Ricochet gets smoked by MVP as he and Kahn tried to jump Bobby Lashley

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cb33ddfb-cc0b-40b7-9e06-cf95c88b4c68/17167.jpg)

