![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/43ccd83b-51d6-4037-ab3e-383d1763e9de/17180.jpg)

FTR says they brought Edge into the company but he made it about himself so they're gonna take care of him at All Out.

Edge says he took the spotlight because the fans gave it to him.

Christian Cage busted Dax Harwood's nose open with a microphone shot and they brawl until security runs out.

FTR hits a guard with a shatter machine. Cope and Cage hit guards with Edgecution and Unprettier.

