![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d034a029-2a5f-416f-9074-476bcea21679/17181.jpg)

*   ## **_AEW Tag Team Championship Ladder Match Qualifier: Young Bucks def. Bang Bang Gang_**
    

The Young Bucks have MONEY again and they don't know how to act

They're paying everyone to be nice to them. They let the money get to their head as they try to pay off Rick Knox but he won't have any of it.

They did pull out the win in the end but they have already spent half of their winnings.

