*   ## **_CMLL's Mascara Dorada def. Beast Mortos to enter the Unified Championship Triple Threat match._**
    

Post match Okada comes out to confront him. Takeshita comes out to confront Okada and then Dorada tried to take them both out.

Dorada only got Okada. But the match is on!

