Kyle Fletcher has taken out Hangman Adam Page the same way he took out Kenny Omega.

*   ## **_Hechicero and Josh Alexander def. Too Flight to earn a spot in the Four Way Tag Team Championship Ladder Match._**
    

They beat down Christopher Daniels. Scorpio Sky and JetSpeed run out to save them. Young Bucks run out to even the odds. Brodido runs out to get involved but the ring clears leaving Daniels alone again

Until Hangman Adam Page runs out to save him. Fletcher attacks Page from behind and beats him down. Page fights back but it's not enough.

Sheer drop brainbuster off the apron, through a table to close September to Remember